    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2325690200" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7525760411530850616">this book was not what i was expecting. not in the least. i went into this thinking it would simply be an action-packed tale of a daring race; but what i got was so, so much more. <br/><br/>i found myself comforted by a story that showed, in a very special way, that sometimes life is not about what you want, but what you need. with lush and poetic prose (which is so on brand for stiefvater), this story weaves together a foundation of desire, love, and strength in a way that tugs at your heartstrings. <br/><br/>wow.</span>
  <span id="freeText7525760411530850616" style="display:none">this book was not what i was expecting. not in the least. i went into this thinking it would simply be an action-packed tale of a daring race; but what i got was so, so much more. <br /><br />i found myself comforted by a story that showed, in a very special way, that sometimes life is not about what you want, but what you need. with lush and poetic prose (which is so on brand for stiefvater), this story weaves together a foundation of desire, love, and strength in a way that tugs at your heartstrings. <br /><br />wow. what a special story. &lt;3<br /><br /><b>↠ <i>4.5 stars</i></b></span>
