  <span id="freeText6845821068036031825" style="display:none"><i>
  <b>“Vices were only vices <br />when looked at through the frame of society.”</b>
</i><br /><br />Another remarkable story delivered by Maggie Stiefvater, there is a surprise! <br /><br />I have a strange relationship with Maggie's characters. I don't just love Ronan Lynch. I love everything that comes with him. I love Chainsaw like it's my pet. I'm protective of his BMW like it's my adopted child. Hell, i even love his boyfriend like i'm his mother. Same goes here: I don't just like Kate and Sean, it's just everything! I'm not sure i can explain it. <br /><br />Full review to come soon.</span>
